<body>
    <h1>Get Space Categories</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"4baec779cfac"><strong>Component type:</strong> Actio=
n</p>
<p local-id=3D"2fd7890fe628"><strong>Category:</strong> Spaces, Rates &amp;=
 Occupancy</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"aaa28da61617" id=3D"GetSpaceCategories-Overview">Overview</=
h2>
<p local-id=3D"3e050cb20abc">The <strong>Get Space Categories</strong> acti=
on retrieves all the space categories (e.g., Standard, Deluxe, Suite) confi=
gured for your property. Space categories define the different types of roo=
ms or spaces available for booking.</p>
<p local-id=3D"2b5fdbb1e75b">You can optionally filter the results by one o=
r more bookable services to retrieve only the categories associated with sp=
ecific services. If no services are selected, categories across all bookabl=
e services are returned.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5ccbd02086f6">The component outputs a list of categories on =
the <strong>out</strong> port, where each item contains an identifier and a=
 display label. This is commonly used as a helper step within a workflow to=
 provide a list of available space categories for downstream actions or con=
ditions =E2=80=94 for example, to check which category a reservation belong=
s to, or to populate a selection in a subsequent step.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"1a59193f-95f6-43cd-9bbe-6297cedeb204">
<h2 local-id=3D"4f0826173abb" id=3D"GetSpaceCategories-InputFields">Input F=
ields</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"619afe68-a758-4232-aec3-f4c=
a1ac010ff" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b08a0985-ae85-47c6-a8ab-1a50cf215ef1">
<th data-local-id=3D"855b68f9-6561-45fc-a468-95149241a234" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"e06a35952f40">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"95d4e7a7-1b04-4a7a-9187-0dd70c32a0df" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"ad4041afb1d2">Required</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"2949748f-5e63-470f-ae1c-942cf79a7063" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"550d0725bda2">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"62ab10ac-c69a-436f-9744-7f42c390e0fd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"4ce0e3ce21c6">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2d09f44a-5702-428d-95e8-b5ba87806f95">
<td data-local-id=3D"4e3ecdf8-7c81-47c0-b856-dba37dc65e9b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3dd34ece8ecd"><strong>Bookable Services</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b9d7a2d5-9fd5-447d-9b9e-a7dd67dcfd90" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e0691fadf00f"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ce761202-511b-45d2-a528-04e29049bacf" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c8913c1a7954">Multi-select dropdown</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"042e369d-43b3-4b07-8b5f-fc2a4145edb6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d77a29bf0ade">Select one or more bookable services to filter=
 the returned space categories. Only categories belonging to the selected s=
ervices will be included in the results. If no services are selected, categ=
ories from all bookable services in the property are returned.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"6b3cb4c3c55a"><strong>Note:</strong> The <strong>Bookable Se=
rvices</strong> dropdown is populated dynamically with the bookable service=
s configured in your property.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"da5146ab-69a9-4eb5-9520-b158be044c03">
<h2 local-id=3D"c63971d47060" id=3D"GetSpaceCategories-OutputFields">Output=
 Fields</h2>
<p local-id=3D"753d9d9d1769">When the space categories are successfully ret=
rieved, the following values are available on the <strong>out</strong> outp=
ut port as an array called <strong>Items</strong>. Each item in the array c=
ontains:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"cbcd7a63-66da-4c56-a601-f68=
7e9aae817" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1bde1397-bfb8-4fb0-9ac6-f615e913a88e">
<th data-local-id=3D"63f3fe9d-1c0d-499d-879f-8a6a70dce103" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1dd9db7236d4">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"eb7d5908-d241-4d4f-8322-cf758d674a0d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"5dd8d267ba66">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"6eea2cb8-a4ea-4b34-8b2c-5314dc91ed97" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"513e5c3b8a51">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6f85e401-47a6-49e8-960d-c6bc157d85ed">
<td data-local-id=3D"de54b44c-1384-44b6-8259-18440e920ee5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d0afdcd07f6c"><strong>Value</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bddd84bb-4772-452a-933e-df5b10d51bb7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e79a0d85b363">Text (GUID)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"878e054f-fb7b-4ae7-9631-4c0bf2e81c19" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"863ed516a8a1">The unique identifier of the space category. T=
his ID can be used in subsequent workflow steps to reference a specific cat=
egory.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"5215649b-915d-4eb0-b617-9e879cf9bef3">
<td data-local-id=3D"81fa7147-fbf5-4c16-b15d-e0e0182dfbca" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a2ed8bbd2fb4"><strong>Label</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c0c2ba8c-064c-4309-8158-c24c880cf92d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1b9f4fde1549">Text</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"07286172-b2f1-41b9-863e-bf6164e49de1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3aaea2d64414">The display name of the space category, locali=
zed to the property's language. If the property has multiple bookable servi=
ces, the service name is appended in parentheses to distinguish categories =
across services (e.g., "Deluxe (Accommodation)").</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"15f0e7a3de4a"><strong>Note:</strong> The label is automatica=
lly localized based on your property's language settings. When multiple boo=
kable services exist, the service name is included in the label to help dis=
tinguish categories that may share the same name across different services.=
</p>
<hr local-id=3D"68c553b2-c300-42fc-95b8-a3fc4ab0b5db">
<h2 local-id=3D"dac1bde3c70e" id=3D"GetSpaceCategories-HowItWorks">How It W=
orks</h2>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"20cb3f1c-ed4c-4083-9e6f-d8633db5dcf5">
<li local-id=3D"1c75b82e-4779-48b1-95bf-4fb1054ffc3f">
<p local-id=3D"d5ffbee9e320">The component receives the optional bookable s=
ervice filter from the input.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a0488d5-c6e6-4a38-a445-eed0c3640cee">
<p local-id=3D"edc6245a6b67">A request is sent to retrieve all active space=
 categories for the property. If one or more bookable services were selecte=
d, only categories associated with those services are returned.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"52651679-7ef5-4a8e-9271-f03ce6aad233">
<p local-id=3D"d05644cc7939">Each category is mapped to a label (display na=
me) and value (unique ID). The label is localized to the property's configu=
red language.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"47704f63-6694-4ed2-ba4a-eba0c927a810">
<p local-id=3D"2eace99cb4c0">If the property has categories across multiple=
 bookable services, the service name is automatically appended to each labe=
l for clarity (e.g., "Standard (Accommodation)" vs. "Standard (Parking)").<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e3ef0d90-4fb8-4cef-811d-1db355e272f4">
<p local-id=3D"769ab1089843">The list of categories is sent to the <strong>=
out</strong> output port as an array of items.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"268fbcae-f703-4aa5-85a0-119f3993de02">
<h2 local-id=3D"a46bd498741d" id=3D"GetSpaceCategories-ExampleUseCases">Exa=
mple Use Cases</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"11c591b3-9f03-408f-814e-5004b956bfe7">
<li local-id=3D"2deb0e03-01a2-4fa1-ab8e-ffe7a61d70ab">
<p local-id=3D"b8881d486fd2"><strong>Filter reservations by category</stron=
g> =E2=80=94 Use Get Space Categories as a reference step to identify the I=
D of a specific category (e.g., "Suite"), then use that ID in a subsequent =
step to filter or route reservations based on their assigned category.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"0c8ba4fd-7b7e-44e8-baf6-35868e27dd8f">
<p local-id=3D"50aedf69e8ab"><strong>Dynamic category selection</strong> =
=E2=80=94 Retrieve all available space categories and pass them to a condit=
ional step that applies different logic depending on the category type (e.g=
., send a welcome email with different content for standard vs. premium cat=
egories).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfe7241e-7cea-42c3-bf5f-3a47c9e7df7e">
<p local-id=3D"196fa2fbbd14"><strong>Service-specific reporting</strong> =
=E2=80=94 Filter categories by a specific bookable service (e.g., only "Acc=
ommodation") to generate reports or trigger actions scoped to a particular =
service offering.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e3140682-3ae1-40d8-ae04-f4d279b838c3">
<h2 local-id=3D"84c49e0b674f" id=3D"GetSpaceCategories-Caching">Caching</h2=
>
<p local-id=3D"43bac13dfdd1">The results of this component are cached to im=
prove performance. Space categories are relatively static data that does no=
t change frequently. If you have recently added or modified space categorie=
s in your property settings, there may be a short delay before the updated =
categories appear in the component's output.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
------=_Part_70_1309351594.1777536505314--
